data.description: Welcome to the market this beautiful, spacious, Split-Level Home! This home features 4 bedroom and 3 bathrooms with over 2,788 Sqft! The interior features beautiful Hardwood floors and an abundance of living and entertaining space. The Kitchen features an oversized Island with Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel appliances and tons of cabinet space! The kitchen opens to a wonderful morning room, the perfect space to enjoy your Morning coffee. This home also features a beautiful sunroom addition that has access to the backyard, morning room and family room. The family room features a brick wall with a cozy fireplace insert with built in shelving. Upstairs has a master suite and two additional bedrooms with a shared bath. Enjoy the large fenced in backyard perfect for entertaining! Near shopping, dining and major commuter locations. you do not want to miss this one!
